{"id":297343,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/06/维权网-杭州两百余访民请愿再被驱逐，警察大打/","date":"2013-06-05T18:45:56Z","modified":"2013-06-05T18:45:56Z","title":"维权网 | 杭州两百余访民请愿再被驱逐，警察大打出手（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员潘好歌报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日上午</span><span>，约两百多位访民再一次到杭州市政府前请愿，但自上个星期三市政府将访民赶到万向公园后，今天仍将访民们赶到了万向公园。尽管如此，警察还对访民大打出手。一对“五八师傅”（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1958</span><span>年随父母下乡的原国家干部的子女）被警察打翻在地，杭州维权人士王丽民见状上前指责警察，杭州拱墅区密渡桥派出所所长和拱墅区巡特警大队大队长等人随即围住王丽民，要把他带走。王责问他犯了何罪，警察怎么能乱抓人？警察说他涉嫌“非法集会”。王说，这些人我都不认识，我只是看到你们对无辜老人施加暴力，才路见不平站出来帮他们说几句公道话，这怎么是非法集会？然而，警察不容分说将王丽民的手反剪在背后，把他押到拱墅区巡特警大队，从上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>点关到下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>点才将他放出，并对他进行了非法搜身。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>王丽民是杭州著名的维权人士，他曾因非法拆迁多次到北京上访，并三次跳过金水桥，多次遭到拘留和毒打。今年他儿子考上育才中学，成绩名列前茅，但在面试时被校方找借口不录取，政府则跟他谈条件，说只要他不上访，政府就可以找育才中学做工作，录取他儿子，这理所当然地遭到王丽民拒绝。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据维权人士朱瑛娣和梁丽婉反映，今天政府出动的警察有一百多人，还有许多便衣混在访民中刺探消息。据了解，杭州市政府近期召开了一次各区公安分局长会议，会上不少分局长挨了批评，说他们维稳不力。所以现在每周请愿的访民都被赶到了万向公园。这是一个值得注意的动向！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-lnQhesZLyzA/Ua9fWqCiBhI/AAAAAAAAjAg/SE_m5dhaZXQ/s1600/501.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-lnQhesZLyzA/Ua9fWqCiBhI/AAAAAAAAjAg/SE_m5dhaZXQ/s320/501.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-GqMbAvV8vxA/Ua9fIfchj1I/AAAAAAAAi_0/RqxeUGL5SAk/s1600/DSC01786.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-GqMbAvV8vxA/Ua9fIfchj1I/AAAAAAAAi_0/RqxeUGL5SAk/s320/DSC01786.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-bq00b3ckZ4U/Ua9fIf1pX7I/AAAAAAAAi_w/YCuYJSCO9p4/s1600/DSC01788.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-bq00b3ckZ4U/Ua9fIf1pX7I/AAAAAAAAi_w/YCuYJSCO9p4/s320/DSC01788.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-eB7nZqxgHwQ/Ua9fNAMG3VI/AAAAAAAAjAA/Ew9VdtsyZVI/s1600/DSC01789.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-eB7nZqxgHwQ/Ua9fNAMG3VI/AAAAAAAAjAA/Ew9VdtsyZVI/s320/DSC01789.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-ZnQQVtk9x6s/Ua9fO04TCNI/AAAAAAAAjAI/F1NoAGbHIrA/s1600/DSC01790.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-ZnQQVtk9x6s/Ua9fO04TCNI/AAAAAAAAjAI/F1NoAGbHIrA/s320/DSC01790.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-1efVvKgHhR0/Ua9fRa3C3zI/AAAAAAAAjAQ/NVw4QIFP5NU/s1600/DSC01803.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-1efVvKgHhR0/Ua9fRa3C3zI/AAAAAAAAjAQ/NVw4QIFP5NU/s320/DSC01803.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-K8jfGvRVaH4/Ua9fUWpLjlI/AAAAAAAAjAY/-l8-y3xBMzk/s1600/DSC01805.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-K8jfGvRVaH4/Ua9fUWpLjlI/AAAAAAAAjAY/-l8-y3xBMzk/s320/DSC01805.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-FRas_ok2nKQ/Ua9faWZqhKI/AAAAAAAAjAo/gnEZHACIPlA/s1600/DSC01806_%25E5%2589%25AF%25E6%259C%25AC.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-FRas_ok2nKQ/Ua9faWZqhKI/AAAAAAAAjAo/gnEZHACIPlA/s320/DSC01806_%25E5%2589%25AF%25E6%259C%25AC.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Hr78pV-N4Vk/Ua9fd